pullRequest.body:
From the FLT project.

When trying to do some calculations on adeles for FLT I realised that the completion of `‚Ñö` at its infinite place was not equal to `‚Ñù` and moreover we basically knew nothing about it. After this PR we at least know which rationals are in its open unit ball (which was what I needed). 

---
